                <head>No. 614<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 12, the United States and Japan signed at Tokyo a Charter Party
                    Agreement for the lease by the United States to Japan of seven patrol frigates.
                    For text, see 3 <gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> (pt. 4) 5183.</p>
                <p>Documents concerning the negotiation of this Agreement are principally in files
                    794.562 and 794.5621 for 1952.</p>
            </div>
